me.jamiemansfield.lorenz.model

Interface Mapping<M extends Mapping>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - The type of the mapping, used for chaining
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClassMapping<M>, FieldMapping, InnerClassMapping, MemberMapping<M>, MethodMapping, TopLevelClassMapping
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractClassMappingImpl, AbstractMappingImpl, AbstractMemberMappingImpl, FieldMappingImpl, InnerClassMappingImpl, MethodMappingImpl, TopLevelClassMappingImpl

    public interface Mapping<M extends Mapping>
    Represents a de-obfuscation mapping for mappable constructs of the Java class format - e.g. classes, fields, and methods.
